    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, so the interior is spotless and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the new-car price tag, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
