      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare, collector-grade example preserved in showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and smoke-free; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the original factory floor mats are pristine. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a complete binder of service records and a recent top-to-bottom fluid service. It sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires and every electronic component functions exactly as intended. This is a turn-key, investment-quality vehicle for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
