      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this beauty! It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely spotless and runs like a dream. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it shows in every single detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
